        recipesMap.put("Nimbu Pani",new String[]{"2 lemons  \n" + "2 cups chilled water  \n" + "2 tbsp sugar (adjust to taste)  \n" + "1/4 tsp black salt  \n" + "1/4 tsp roasted cumin powder  \n" + "A few mint leaves (optional)  \n" + "Ice cubes  \n" + "\n" + "★ Direction Of Use  ★\n" + "\n" + "1. Prepare the Lemon Mixture:  \n" + "Squeeze the juice of lemons into a bowl. Add sugar, black salt, and roasted cumin powder. Mix until the sugar dissolves.  \n" + "\n" + "2. Mix and Serve:\n" + "Add the lemon mixture to chilled water. Stir well.  \n" + "Pour into glasses, add ice cubes, and garnish with mint leaves if desired.  \n" + "\n" + "Enjoy your refreshing Nimbu Pani! \uD83C\uDF4B✨"});

